data=read.table('DATACIGARETTE-1.txt',header = TRUE)
mm = lm(Sales~ Age+HS+Income+Black+Female+ Price,data = data)
a = summary(mm)
lm(Sales~Age,data = data)

#(d)
sresi = rstudent(mm)
plot(sresi,ylab = 'studentized residual')
text(which(abs(sresi)>2),sresi[which(abs(sresi)>2)]*0.9,labels = which(abs(sresi)>2))

#(e)
lev = hatvalues(mm)# lev = hat(model.matrix(mm))
plot(lev)
text(which(lev>0.2),lev[which(lev>0.2)]*0.9,labels = which(lev>0.2))

#(f)
cook = cooks.distance(mm)
plot(cook,ylab="Cooks distances")
points(which(cook>1),cook[which(cook>1)],col='red')

data=read.csv('Oildata-2.csv')
full = lm(Mileage~.,data = data)

reduced = lm(Mileage~Rgasoline,data = data)
anova(reduced,full)
## Analysis of Variance Table
